{
  "stem": "17330.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 200.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were in the city to buy something, that was my first husband and my second husband and his wife and their baby.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Karel and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Karel Abram.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the-- and his parents were--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bluma Abram and Philip Abram.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came out of the city and we were warned through Jewish people, go back, because in the next street they pick the men up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were desperate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have a clue what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we hide somewhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the baby was in a pram, so we were stuck with the pram.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have food for the baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have nappies, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then my husband or what was then my friend said, across the street where they were picking up the boys, there is a guy I worked for, because he learned to be [INAUDIBLE] building.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, I'll go to those people when it's quiet and ask them if they'll keep the pram.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we picked up a cab and went to my mother's-in-law place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there we put towels on the baby, because we didn't have nappies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stayed 'til it was dark, and then they went home to their place and I went to my place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and then I decided I'm not going to wait to be picked up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, I'll go in hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my first husband, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he worked for a while for my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had red hair, so from a mile away you could see him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he worked in Limburg, that is south of Holland, of Amsterdam so to speak.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he went there, did some traveling.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
